# AgentHub

## Multi-Agent AI Orchestration Desktop Platform

Version: 1.0

Status: Architecture & Implementation Specification

---

# 1. Executive Summary

AgentHub is a privacy-first desktop platform that orchestrates multiple AI coding agents and AI assistants through a unified workflow engine.

The platform enables:

* Claude Code CLI
* Grok CLI
* GitHub Copilot CLI
* Antigravity CLI
* Local Ollama Agents
* Future MCP-compatible Agents

to collaborate on software development tasks while maintaining strict control over source code exposure.

AgentHub is designed as a workflow orchestration platform rather than a chat application.

---

# 2. Product Vision

## Problem Statement

Developers currently use multiple AI coding assistants independently.

Problems:

* Context switching between tools
* Duplicate work
* No coordinated workflow
* No centralized audit trail
* Limited privacy control
* No proactive automation

## Solution

AgentHub provides:

* Multi-agent coordination
* Privacy-aware context management
* Workflow automation
* Audit logging
* Proactive monitoring
* Local-first architecture

